mother( X, Y) :- parent( X, Y), female( X).
grandparent(X,Z):-parent(X,Y),parent(Y,Z).
sister(X,Y):-parent(Z,X),parent(Z,Y),female(X),X\=Y.
hasachild(X):-parent(_,_).
somebody-has-child :- parent( _, _).
